 ğŸŸ¢ Real-time Selenium example

```java
class LoginPage {

    String url;
    static String browser = "Chrome";

    LoginPage(String url){
        this.url = url;
    }

    void open(){
        System.out.println("Opening " + url + " in " + browser);
    }
}

public class TestRun {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        LoginPage lp = new LoginPage("https://google.com");
        lp.open();
    }
}
```

